3. cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity) - The paper involves measuring physiological measures to develop an estimation of users' mental load, which can be used to design more secure systems that take into account the mental load of users.
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper involves measuring physiological measures to develop an estimation of users' mental load, which can be used to design more effective social and information networks that take into account the mental load of users.
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper involves analyzing physiological measures to develop an estimation of users' mental load, which can be done using machine learning techniques.
